(7, 1, '2015-06-22 10:05:12', '2015-06-22 10:05:12', '', 'About', 'The Interaction Design Lab brings together the research interests and expertise in the field of interactive systems and applications from the design area. We see ourselves as partners in business and academia. Our aim is to design, develop and pioneer new forms of interactive systems, objects and spaces. Here, you can find a list of our current research topics.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2015-06-28 23:15:21', '2015-06-28 23:15:21', '', 0, 'http://jordi.local:8888/fhp/idl/?page_id=7', 2, 'page', '', 0),
